title: U Fest Co Sign Concert
desc: Bringing together some of the UK's most exciting musical artists on one stage with a full light show and an 18 meter cinema screen. Doors open at 5pm and show starts at 6pm Performances and DJ sets by  Naughty Boy ,  Lady Leshurr ,  Big Narstie ,  Fekky ,  Section Boyz ,  Afro B ,  Mo Stack ,  Compozers ,  Big Tipper  plus lots of surprises. Expect the Copperbox arena to be transformed into an epic night of hi-tech visuals and the best of London music. These Tickets are standing. +14, though the event is about the positive movement of youth culture, there may be some strong language. For more updates on this event:  WW.UFESTLDN.COM
